{
  "__inputs": [],
  "__requires": [],
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "description": "SRE event history, remediation log, scale-out events and recommendations",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "Edge Overview",
      "url": "/d/edge-overview",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "dashboard"
    }
  ],
  "panels": [

    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Alert Timeline",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "collapsed": false
    },

    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Alert Severity Over Time",
      "description": "Shows which severity levels fired and when",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "warning threshold" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "dash": [10, 10], "fill": "dash" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "moderate threshold" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "dash": [10, 10], "fill": "dash" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "critical threshold" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "dash": [10, 10], "fill": "dash" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "emergency threshold" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "purple", "mode": "fixed" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "dash": [5, 5], "fill": "dash" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "edge_processing_latency_ms{job=\"edge_nodes\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{ zone }} latency"
        },
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "vector(60)",
          "legendFormat": "warning threshold"
        },
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "vector(75)",
          "legendFormat": "moderate threshold"
        },
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "vector(85)",
          "legendFormat": "critical threshold"
        },
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "vector(95)",
          "legendFormat": "emergency threshold"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Scale-Out Events",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 9 },
      "collapsed": false
    },

    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Times VM3 Was Activated",
      "description": "Total scale-out events since monitoring started",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green",  "value": 0 },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 3 },
              { "color": "red",    "value": 5 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "count_over_time(edge_heartbeat{zone=\"standby\"}[24h] == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "activations"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Emergency Alerts",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 10 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green",  "value": 0 },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red",    "value": 3 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "count_over_time(ALERTS{severity=\"emergency\",alertstate=\"firing\"}[24h])",
          "legendFormat": "emergencies"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Average Recovery Time (min)",
      "description": "Average time from emergency alert to latency below warning",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 10 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["mean"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "m",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green",  "value": 0  },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5  },
              { "color": "red",    "value": 10 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "avg(edge_processing_latency_ms{job=\"edge_nodes\"}) / 60 * 0",
          "legendFormat": "N/A"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Current System State",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 10 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "options": { "0": { "text": "NORMAL",    "color": "green"  } }, "type": "value" },
            { "options": { "1": { "text": "SCALE-OUT", "color": "orange" } }, "type": "value" }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green",  "value": 0 },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "edge_heartbeat{zone=\"standby\"} or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "state"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "VM3 Standby — Unheard Zone 3 Sensors",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "collapsed": false
    },

    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Zone 3 Sensor Message Rate — Publishing But No Listener",
      "description": "Zone 3 sensors are always publishing. This graph goes flat (zero) because nobody is listening — until VM3 activates.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 },
          "color": { "fixedColor": "blue", "mode": "fixed" }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": "Prometheus",
          "expr": "rate(edge_messages_received_total{zone=\"standby\"}[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "zone3 messages received by VM3"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Remediation Recommendations",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "collapsed": false
    },

    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Graduated Response Reference",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Graduated Alert Response\n\n| Threshold | Severity | Automated Action |\n|-----------|----------|------------------|\n| **60%** | ⚠️ Warning | Notification only — log event |\n| **75%** | 🟠 Moderate | Run `edge-tune.yml` — local optimizations |\n| **85%** | 🔴 Critical | Run `load-redistribute.yml` — reduce sensor rate |\n| **95%** | 🟣 Emergency | Human Override — Telegram 60s countdown |\n\n## Scale-Out Logic\n- VM3 powers on when emergency fires\n- VM3 handles the most overloaded zone\n- Both VM1+VM2 overloaded → VM3 helps most critical, Telegram sent for second\n- After recovery: VM3 powers off automatically via `scale-in.yml`\n\n## Error Budget\n- SLA Target: **99.9%**\n- Monthly budget: **43.8 minutes** of downtime allowed\n- Burn rate alert: fires when consuming > **2x** budget per hour"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 32,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Demo Commands",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 23 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Chaos Engineering Demo\n\n```bash\n# Trigger warning (60ms latency)\nansible-playbook latency-simulate.yml \\\n  -e \"target_host=edge-node-1 latency_ms=80\"\n\n# Trigger critical (85ms latency)\nansible-playbook latency-simulate.yml \\\n  -e \"target_host=edge-node-1 latency_ms=120\"\n\n# Trigger emergency (95ms latency)\nansible-playbook latency-simulate.yml \\\n  -e \"target_host=edge-node-1 latency_ms=200\"\n\n# Or use stress mode on sensors\n./virtual-sensors/sensors-generate.sh stress zone1\n```\n\n## Recovery\n```bash\n# Remove injected latency\nansible-playbook latency-remove.yml \\\n  -e \"target_host=edge-node-1\"\n\n# Restore normal sensor rate\n./virtual-sensors/sensors-generate.sh normal zone1\n```"
      }
    }

  ],
  "refresh": "15s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "tags": ["edge", "sre", "events"],
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "SRE — Recommendations & Events",
  "uid": "sre-recommendations",
  "version": 1
}
